text: I take only salads over there now, but in past i tried chicken and vegetables, really tasty food over there actualy, try greek salad!

text: The food is very good, but the 2 girls working in the morning either hate their job or people In general. Anyway, they should not be working in any customer service kind of business. Very unwelcoming experience.
